TIPS FOR NEW PLAYERS

  - Type help getting-started and read help combat before fighting.
  - introduce yourself in social scenes so others know your name.
  - tune your radio to a party frequency and use radio to coordinate.
  - rest to heal between fights. watch your thirst and status on score.
  - explore Praxis first, then travel via Moxim's rifts to other regions.
  - use bug and typo when you find problems; staff appreciate reports.

